channel.title: G! Turbo - But there's a twist - The Unseen, The Mercenary, The Doppelganger and The Dad win!
channel.description:
* It will start most likely 5 minutes after it fills. * Days are 15 minutes. Twilight is 2 minutes. Nights are 5 minutes, unless I’m a failure and extend it. * Early day actions will be processed during the day, late day actions will be processed during Twilight, due to me being a failure once more. * There can be more than one King, but only a King election will take place once there are no Kings remaining. * I’m on PC, so don’t have mercy, feel free to make me want to die. * The amount of players are infinite but there must be at least 7 players.
1. Kai_5 2. Mercenary 3. Psycho 4. ~~Insanity~~ - **Dead** 5. Eevee 6. ~~Soulshade~~ - **Dead** 7. Geyde 8. Firekitten 9. ~~Isaac~~ - **Dead** 10. Squid
# The Line for the classes using in this is 1481 (as of game start)
Classes will be watered down if they are not able to be used in Turbo, if classes can not work in turbo situations like this, they will be re-rolled.
